OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,FA coroner has raised concerns about
OL,7,Fhow police forces respond when staff
OL,8,Fexpress suicidal thoughts after a
OL,9,Fstudent officer took his own life.
OL,11,FAnugrah Abraham, from Bury in Greater
OL,12,FManchester, was training with West
OL,13,FYorkshire Police in Halifax when he
OL,14,Fwas found dead in woodland in March
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FClaims by his family that the 21-year-
OL,18,Fold - known as "Anu" - was the victim
OL,19,Fof bullying and racism were denied by
OL,20,Fthe force.
