OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,FThe coroner wrote: "The subsequent
OL,7,Femail to Anu in no way was reflective
OL,8,Fof a caring approach to an individual
OL,9,Fwho was expressing suicidal thoughts."
OL,11,FAddressing the National Police Chiefs
OL,12,FCouncil in her report, Ms Kearsley
OL,13,Fsaid the court heard there had been an
OL,14,F"increase in mental health issues
OL,15,Famongst police officers nationally".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
