OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,FShe added: "Despite this, the question
OL,7,Fof what imminent adjustments should be
OL,8,Fmade or considered once an officer
OL,9,Fdiscloses suicidal thoughts, was
OL,10,Funclear... In this case Anu's mental
OL,11,Fdeterioration was reportedly directly
OL,12,Flinked to his role as a police officer.
OL,14,F"It is acknowledged that this is a
OL,15,Fdifficult issue and there will be
OL,16,Fissues such as confidentiality to
OL,17,Fconsider."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
