OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,FMs Kearsley also raised concerns that
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police does not have a
OL,8,Fregistered mental health nurse,
OL,9,Fdespite the fact that "most
OL,10,Foccupational health unit (OHU)
OL,11,Freferrals within police forces now
OL,12,Frelate to mental health issues as
OL,13,Fopposed to physical health issues".
OL,15,FShe said there had been "no
OL,16,Finvestigation into the quality of care
OL,17,Fafforded to (Mr Abraham) by the OHU
OL,18,Fwithin WYP".
