OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,F"Hence at the time of the inquest,
OL,7,Fthere had been no reflection by
OL,8,Fpractitioners as to the quality of
OL,9,Fcare provided and no learning in
OL,10,Frespect of processes and procedures,"
OL,11,Fshe added.
OL,13,F"It was accepted that following the
OL,14,Finquest there were matters which would
OL,15,Fbe considered. The lack of
OL,16,Finvestigation meant learning from
OL,17,Fdeaths in order to prevent future
OL,18,Fdeaths was not addressed."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
