OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,FMr Abraham was on a Police Constable
OL,7,FDegree Apprenticeship (PCDA) when he
OL,8,Fdied. Ms Kearsley said witnesses at
OL,9,Fthe inquest had spoken of the impact
OL,10,Fof undertaking a PCDA "including the
OL,11,Flevels of stress they incurred".
OL,13,FThe family's solicitor Daniel Cooper
OL,14,Fsaid: "The concerns raised by the
OL,15,Fcoroner in today's report reflect what
OL,16,FAnu's family have maintained
OL,17,Fthroughout these inquest proceedings,
OL,18,Fnamely that West Yorkshire Police were
OL,19,Fnot able to effectively respond to
OL,20,FAnu's repeated calls for support with
OL,21,Fhis mental health.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
