OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F368A1737081370
OL,3,CCoroner raises concerns about police
OL,4,Cmental health after trainee's suicide
OL,6,F"Their inability to support Anu comes
OL,7,Fat a time when more and more young
OL,8,Fpolice officers around the country are
OL,9,Ffacing increasing stress and mental
OL,10,Fillness at work.
OL,12,F"Action must be taken by the force,
OL,13,Fand the Police Chiefs Council and
OL,14,FCollege of Policing, to address the
OL,15,Fshortcomings identified in this awful
OL,16,Fcase."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
