OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We will work
OL,8,Fclosely with our partners, including
OL,9,Fthe College and Policing, and at West
OL,10,FYorkshire Police, to progress and
OL,11,Fconsider the coroner's
OL,12,Frecommendations."
